{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0001", "text": "愛也要講資格 我有什麼資格", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 5, 4, 9, 3, 4, 5, 5, 2, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["oi3", "jaa5", "jiu3", "gong2", "zi1", "gaak3", "ngo5", "jau5", "sam6", "mo1", "zi1", "gaak3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "講", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "資格", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "資格", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "自己保重", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5796", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0002", "text": "你若靠向她 總可算合理抉擇", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 4, 3, 9, 9, 4, 2, 5, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "joek6", "kaau3", "hoeng3", "taa1", "zung2", "ho2", "syun3", "hap6", "lei5", "kyut3", "zaak6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "靠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "向", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "總可算", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "合理", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抉擇", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "自己保重", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5796", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0003", "text": "我每晚都咳嗽 自你有最新好友", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 5, 3, 3, 4, 2, 5, 5, 4, 3, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "mui5", "maan5", "dou1", "kat1", "sau3", "zi6", "nei5", "jau5", "zeoi3", "san1", "hou2", "jau5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "每晚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "咳嗽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最新", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好友", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "自己保重", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5796", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0004", "text": "但你偏痛切慰問 病菌怎麼會纏身", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 4, 4, 4, 2, 2, 9, 9, 3, 0, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "nei5", "pin1", "tung3", "cai3", "wai3", "man6", "beng6", "kwan2", "zam2", "mo1", "cin4", "san1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "偏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "痛切", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "慰問", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "病菌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "纏身", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "自己保重", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5796", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0005", "text": "我若再依戀你 定會加重我這病情", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 3, 9, 5, 2, 3, 5, 5, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "joek6", "zoi3", "ji1", "lyun2", "nei5", "ding6", "gaa1", "ngo5", "ze5", "beng6", "cing4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "依戀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "定", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "加重", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "病情", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "自己保重", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5796", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
